flowchart LR
    IN[Input sample] --> DL[Delay line]
    DL --> PRE[Symmetric pre-add]
    PRE --> DSP0[DSP stage 0]
    COEF[Coeff / tap regs] --> DSP0
    DSP0 --> REG0[Pipe regs]
    REG0 --> DSPK[DSP stage 1..k]
    DSPK --> ACC[Systolic accum chain]
    ACC --> QS[Round / Saturate]
    QS --> OUT[Output]
